cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and proposes a hierarchical recurrent neural network model for predicting situation entity types of clauses based on context-aware clause representations. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with modeling context influences and inter-dependencies of clauses, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
